COLLECT JEWELS TO WIN MONEY, 
JACKPOTS OR FREE SPINS

COLLECT JEWELS TO WIN MONEY, 
JACKPOTS OR FREE SPINS

Changing the bet will reset the
jewel board.
The jewel board state is saved on all
bets. Come back to this bet to continue
from where it was left off.
THAT’S THE WAY I LIKE IT
OH MY, THAT WIN IS SO BIG!
OH MY, THAT WIN IS SO BIG!
All symbols pay from left to right on adjacent reels starting from the leftmost reel.
WILD symbol appears on reels 2, 3, 4 and 5.
This is the WILD and substitutes for all symbols except for        ,        .
Wins awarded for left to right adjacent symbol combinations.
Random jewels appear on top of reels 2, 3 and 4. At every spin, the jewels change with new jewels dropping from the top.
The jewels can have one of the following awards:
Money value between 5x total bet and 200x total bet.
Fixed JACKPOT values of 25x bet for MINOR Jackpot, 100x bet for MAJOR Jackpot and 2000x bet for GRAND Jackpot.
A number of free games from 8 to 100. They also award 1x total bet when collected.
Possible values are: 5x, 6.25x, 7.5x, 10x, 12x, 15x, 16x, 18x, 20x, 25x, 30x, 40x, 50x, 60x, 75x, 80x, 100x or 200x total bet.
It appears only on reels 1 and 5.
This is the CONGO CASH symbol.
It appears only on reels 2, 3 and 4.
When two BUTTERFLY symbols hit on reel 1 and 5 along with at least one CONGO CASH symbol on reels 2, 3 and 4 the value on the jewel on top of the reel with the CONGO CASH symbols is awarded.
Up to 3 jewels can be collected on the same spin.
The jewel board is saved for every possible bet and returning to a certain bet will load the saved jewel board.
Changing the bet after a jewel board has been saved will reset it to default values.
Trigger the FREE GAMES round by collecting at least one free games jewel.
The round starts with the total number of free games collected from all jewels.
The jewel board is active during the FREE GAMES round.
Special reels are in play during the feature.
During the round, at least one WILD is guaranteed to hit on every free spin on the reel from where the free spins jewel was collected
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher
Only the highest win is paid per winning combination on the same pay way.
When winning on multiple pay ways, all wins are added to the total win.
Free spins and bonus wins are added to the payline win.
All wins are multiplied by base bet.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
Free spins win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
Free spins total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.

Click the             button to open the bet menu. Select the bet you want to use in the game by adjusting values using the           and           buttons.
Press the SPIN button to play.
opens the menu that contains the settings which affect the way the game is being played.
takes you to the casino lobby

toggles sound and music on and off

CREDIT and BET labels show the current balance and current total bet.
Click on the labels to switch between coins view and cash view.
button to open the Autoplay menu
Drag pages up and down to scroll between information pages
The bet menu shows the number of lines available in the game, and the current total bet in both coins and cash.
Use the          and          buttons in the COINS PER LINE and COIN VALUE fields to change the values.
Click on the buttons showing the number of possible auto-spins to start Autoplay
SKIP SCREENS option auto-skips the feature introduction and end screens after a short period of time
ON ANY WIN – whenever you win something, the Autoplay function stops
IF FEATURE IS WON – whenever a feature like bonus game or free spins is won, Autoplay will stop
IF SINGLE WIN EXCEEDS – whenever a single win is above the sum written in this field, the Autoplay function stops
IF CASH INCREASES BY – whenever your current balance is above the sum written in this field, the Autoplay function stops
IF CASH DECREASES BY – whenever your current balance is below the sum written in this field, the Autoplay function stops
START AUTOPLAY – starts the Autoplay function
